name: malonyl-CoA:acetyl-CoA malonyltransferase (2-hydroxy-5-methyl-1-naphthoic acid forming)
definition: Acetyl-CoA + 5 Malonyl-CoA + 2 NADPH + 2 H+ <=> 2-Hydroxy-5-methyl-1-naphthoate + 6 CoA + 5 CO2 + 3 H2O + 2 NADP+
